 unrestrained swordsman Huo Zhanbai seeks medicine for a friend's child and encounters the pharmacist Xue Ziye. Over eight years of daily interaction, they progress from having their own convictions to deepening understanding, mutual redemption, and a promise to meet under a plum tree the following year. However, due to the responsibilities they bear, they find it difficult to express their love, leaving behind a regret of eternal separation. Amidst the joyous toasts in the snowy night and a farewell across a thousand miles, a poignant and unforgettable missed opportunity unfolds—a love destined to be unable to endure, depicting a tale of redemption and letting go in a life-and-death romance.","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"263037","season":1,"vote_average":9.8,"vote_count":4},"modified":"2024-10-24T22:48:50.000Z","cast":["Lý Thấm","Tăng Thuấn Hy","Vương Hoằng Nghị","Trần Hạo Sâm","Jin Zehao","Ji Shuyi","Tăng Khả Ny"],"director":["Leung Sing-Kuen","Ren Haitao"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Lý Thấm","name_vi":"Lý Thấm","name_original":"Li Qin","tmdb_id":568304,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/thak4pt7jCPbl2xx5HnFhkEE0Tu.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/568304"},{"name":"Tăng Thuấn Hy","name_vi":"Tăng Thuấn Hy","name_original":"Joseph Zeng","tmdb_id":1803092,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hfMNwzZv7SxJ6d8gk8rhPZdg4C8.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1803092"},{"name":"Vương Hoằng Nghị","name_vi":"Vương Hoằng Nghị","name_original":"Wang Hongyi","tmdb_id":3715156,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6rUH7NxarCBHRDbSmtPisgJq7pn.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3715156"},{"name":"Trần Hạo Sâm","name_vi":"Trần Hạo Sâm","name_original":"Edward Chen","tmdb_id":1834631,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dOyZVinKyxAcyGFSYC8slGV7JtV.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1834631"},{"name":"Jin Zehao","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jin Zehao","tmdb_id":2417157,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.